{"tid":1034751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九啟動葡萄園計劃 唐英年:成打卡勝地","createTime":"2019-02-24T07:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T09:14:06.000Z","uid":64345,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c1be153131c6537f21c21b47a2613fe6f158d9","tid":1034751,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"西九文化區管理局昨日在西九文化區苗圃公園，舉行葡萄種植儀式，標誌葡萄園計劃正式啟動。葡萄園將設於西九藝術公園臨海的觀景平台之上。<br />\n<br />\n管理局董事局主席唐英年表示，這次葡萄種植活動標誌管理局正式展開探討過程，向法國布艮第酒莊的莊主請教在西九建設臨海葡萄園的可能性。他續稱，隨着計劃開展，香港將打造一個獨一無二的葡萄園，將成為訪客必到的Instagram取景勝地。<br />\n<br />\n除了黑皮諾以外，管理局將按一貫做法於苗圃公園試行種植霞多麗(Chardonnay)及梅洛(Merlot)等不同品種的葡萄樹，如果能適應西九風土，將被遷移至藝術公園永久種植。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2065594/%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E5%9C%92%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83+%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%B9%B4%3A%E6%88%90%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%E5%8B%9D%E5%9C%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2065594%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2591%25A1%25E8%2590%2584%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%2B%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4%253A%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%259C%25B0&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=7b1f808a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2065594/%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E5%9C%92%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83+%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%B9%B4%3A%E6%88%90%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%E5%8B%9D%E5%9C%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唐唐瘋狂飲紅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594e16e8bade466424d8ffabc4945f5c799075a3","tid":1034751,"uid":41655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj